      MOVE THROUGH DOOMED STATIONS LIKE A PHANTOM, SPECIALIZING IN HIGH-STAKES SURVIVAL
      WHERE OTHERS SEE ONLY ANNIHILATION.
    characterSprite: {fileID: -1721454704, guid: 8642032d1ae8ee746a36f32ba6b71c8c,
      type: 3}
  - characterName: THE HIGH-ROLLER
    characterDescription: A RICH PSYCHOTIC SEEKING THE ULTIMATE SPECTACLE. THEY HAVE
      TRADED THEIR FORTUNE FOR A SEAT AT THE TABLE WHERE THE STAKES ARE SUPERNOVAE
      AND BLACK HOLES. TO THEM, SURVIVAL IS THE ONLY LUXURY LEFT.
    characterSprite: {fileID: -1316832831, guid: 8642032d1ae8ee746a36f32ba6b71c8c,
      type: 3}
  - characterName: THE PYROMANIAC
    characterDescription: AN EXPLOSIVES EXPERT WHO FINDS BEAUTY IN CRITICAL FAILURES.
      THEY DON'T JUST PLAY THE GAME; THEY WORSHIP THE CHAOS. THEY ARE AT HOME WHERE
      THE FLOOR IS LAVA AND THE CLOCK IS TICKING.
    characterSprite: {fileID: -1161104255, guid: 8642032d1ae8ee746a36f32ba6b71c8c,
      type: 3}
  - characterName: THE PUNK
    characterDescription: A REBEL FROM THE CRACKING DOMES OF THE LAST CITY. THEY
      SEE THE GAME AS THE ONLY HONEST SPORT LEFT. THEY ARE HERE TO BLAST THE ELITE
      AND PROVE THAT GRIT OUTLASTS GOLD WHEN THE UNIVERSE ENDS.
    characterSprite: {fileID: -1656477654, guid: 8642032d1ae8ee746a36f32ba6b71c8c,
      type: 3}
  - characterName: THE ENFORCER
    characterDescription: A DISGRACED SECURITY CHIEF FROM A COLLAPSING SECTOR. THEY
      TREAT EVERY DOOMED ARENA AS A FINAL RIOT TO BE QUELLED. IN A GALAXY FALLING
      APART, THEY INTEND TO BE THE LAST AUTHORITY STANDING.
    characterSprite: {fileID: 1267943911, guid: 8642032d1ae8ee746a36f32ba6b71c8c,
      type: 3}
